damage that Nadeisco did

3
00:00:20,687 --> 00:00:22,397
while breaking through
the big barrier.

4
00:00:22,523 --> 00:00:24,483
But it must have
been quite a bit.

5
00:00:24,566 --> 00:00:26,226
With all the action
violence however,

6
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,610
there was also love.

7
00:00:27,694 --> 00:00:29,744
And there is no greater
love than that of those

8
00:00:29,863 --> 00:00:32,283
who give their lives so
that others may carry on.

9
00:00:32,366 --> 00:00:34,026
Thank you Mr. Yamada.

