503
00:21:56,649 --> 00:21:59,069
‐ [Announcer] Oh the
bittersweet seeds of fate.

504
00:21:59,151 --> 00:22:01,571
Yurika runs, unable
to face the truth

505
00:22:01,654 --> 00:22:02,864
